  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Death Harvest</strong> is a gritty, cooperative VR survival shooter set in a post-apocalyptic world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >full of zombies. As a survivor of Boston’s combat unit “The Reapers”, you are all that</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >stands between colony survival and collapse.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive the danger, solo or squad</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a lone wolf or running up to a 4 player squad, no mission is trivial. Explore the post-apocalyptic world with real-time changing weather where danger can be around any corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/11d7e207acdb81f0aa93a942d295c8ee.poster.avif?t=1774265907\" width=720 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/11d7e207acdb81f0aa93a942d295c8ee.webm?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/11d7e207acdb81f0aa93a942d295c8ee.mp4?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game modes packed with adrenaline</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge, kill and come back alive. Choose one of three game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Loot & Extract</strong>: Scavenge resources and come back to the base when you decide it’s too dangerous to linger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Seek & Destroy</strong>: Hunt for a high value target.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Wave Survival</strong>: Hold the line against the horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/3c3ff4f52e0fc793ebb38e939bac7535.poster.avif?t=1774265907\" width=720 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/3c3ff4f52e0fc793ebb38e939bac7535.webm?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/3c3ff4f52e0fc793ebb38e939bac7535.mp4?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Large variety of weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master selection of weapons and fight to live another day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>25 realistic firearms</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>16 melee weapons</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>3 explosive types</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/edf009c35448fea9f480b0e162a0f40c.poster.avif?t=1774265907\" width=720 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/edf009c35448fea9f480b0e162a0f40c.webm?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/edf009c35448fea9f480b0e162a0f40c.mp4?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meaningful VR interactions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the world through many VR interactions like:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Manual management of items in the backpack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Interaction with datapad through the touchscreen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Eating and drinking to increase chances of survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Many other minor physical interactions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/dc1be93db2953ff6ee1f07af64a43071.poster.avif?t=1774265907\" width=720 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/dc1be93db2953ff6ee1f07af64a43071.webm?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/dc1be93db2953ff6ee1f07af64a43071.mp4?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Uncover the world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your actions leave a mark on this world! Help survivors and uncover the story of the virus outbreak through colony development and environmental storytelling</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/d8bc2d8adb286cf41a8bc08925e9a6b9.poster.avif?t=1774265907\" width=720 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/d8bc2d8adb286cf41a8bc08925e9a6b9.webm?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/d8bc2d8adb286cf41a8bc08925e9a6b9.mp4?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bear the responsibility for the colony’s survival and venture into the unknown filled with</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >danger to reclaim what’s left of the old world!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI usage</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice generation </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Language translations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Death Harvest</strong> is a gritty, cooperative VR survival shooter set in a post-apocalyptic world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >full of zombies. As a survivor of Boston’s combat unit “The Reapers”, you are all that</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >stands between colony survival and collapse.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive the danger, solo or squad</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a lone wolf or running up to a 4 player squad, no mission is trivial. Explore the post-apocalyptic world with real-time changing weather where danger can be around any corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/11d7e207acdb81f0aa93a942d295c8ee.poster.avif?t=1774265907\" width=720 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/11d7e207acdb81f0aa93a942d295c8ee.webm?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/11d7e207acdb81f0aa93a942d295c8ee.mp4?t=1774265907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game modes packed with adrenaline</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge, kill and come back alive. Choose one of three game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Loot & Extract</strong>: Scavenge resources and come back to the base when you decide it’s too dangerous to linger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Seek & Destroy</strong>: Hunt for a high value target.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Wave Survival</strong>: Hold the line against the horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st